hich%20was%20valued%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20%2420%20billion%20in%20a%20funding%20round%20last%20year%2C%20will%20launch%20the%20product.%20If%20it%20does%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperplexity-shifts-to-subscriptions-business-growth-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewould%20put%20Perplexity%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20originally%20focused%20on%20an%20AI-powered%20search%20engine%20that%20competes%20with%20Google%20%E2%80%94%20much%20closer%20to%20vying%20for%20supremacy%20with%20Cursor%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20OpenAI%2C%20all%20of%20which%20have%20built%20widely-used%20AI%20coding%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeammate%20is%20meant%20to%20oversee%20software%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eprojects%20from%20start%20to%20finish%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20announcement%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20built%20for%20long-horizon%20engineering%20work%3A%20owning%20projects%2C%20investigating%20issues%2C%20and%20monitoring%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20announcement%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Perplexity%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperplexity-makes-200-ai-browser-free-to-battle-ai-slop-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPerplexity%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20given%20the%20tool%20tasks%20such%20as%20finding%20bugs%20in%20internal%20systems%2C%20screenshots%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20tool%20is%20model-agnostic%2C%20meaning%20that%20it's%20not%20built%20on%20any%20particular%20chatbot%2C%20the%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerplexity's%20chief%20technology%20officer%2C%20Denis%20Yarats%2C%20has%20also%20urged%20the%20startup's%20engineers%20to%20use%20AI%20for%20coding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20before%20Teammate%20launched%20internally%2C%20the%20executive%20wrote%20in%20messages%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20that%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20or%20sooner%2C%20software%20engineers%20should%20%26quot%3Bstop%20looking%20at%20code%26quot%3B%20and%20just%20use%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYarats%20also%20defended%20AI%20against%20accusations%20that%20it%20produces%20%26quot%3Bslop%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20poor-quality%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSlop%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20a%20thing%26quot%3B%20as%20long%20as%20the%20code%20it%20generates%20passes%20quality%20checks%2C%20Yarats%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20Charles%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acrollet%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ecrollet%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20on%20Signal%20and%20WhatsApp%20at%20%3Cu%3E628-282-2811%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3Cem%3E%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecure-news-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperplexity-building-ai-coding-tool-take-on-cursor-and-openai-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783466529000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d78be965805a2c542de3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperplexity-building-ai-coding-tool-take-on-cursor-and-openai-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22San%20Francisco-based%20Perplexity%2C%20valued%20at%20%2420%20billion%2C%20is%20working%20on%20'Teammate%2C'%20an%20AI%20tool%20that%20may%20compete%20with%20AI%20coding%20giants%20like%20Anthropic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22crollet%40insider.com%20(Charles%20Rollet)%22%2C%2