es%20in%20severance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225789%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Microsoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d6aed94175b768171fdbf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224044%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMicrosoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella.%3Cp%3ESven%20Hoppe%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMicrosoft%20is%20offering%20up%20to%2039%20weeks%20of%20severance%20to%20most%20laid-off%20US%20employees.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20on%20Monday%20announced%20plans%20to%20lay%20off%20around%204%2C800%20employees.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20severance%20offer%20is%20similar%20to%20Microsoft's%20recent%20voluntary%20retirement%20buyout%20program.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20is%20offering%20laid-off%20US%20employees%20up%20to%2039%20weeks'%20base%20pay%20for%20most%20US%20employees%2C%20according%20to%20severance%20offers%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20on%20Monday%20announced%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-jobs-cuts-across-sales-and-xbox-read-the-memo-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elay%20off%20around%204%2C800%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%202.1%25%20of%20its%20global%20workforce%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-job-cuts-layoffs-sales-consulting-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Econfirming%20Business%20Insider's%20earlier%20report%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20severance%20package%20includes%20a%20minimum%20of%2060%20days%20of%20base%20pay%2C%20during%20which%20employees%20will%20remain%20on%20the%20payroll%2C%20up%20to%20a%20maximum%20of%2039%20weeks%20of%20base%20pay%20for%20most%20employees%2C%20based%20on%20seniority%20and%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20at%20internal%20levels%2064%20and%20below%20will%20receive%20one%20week%20of%20base%20pay%20per%20six%20months%20of%20service%2C%20and%20employees%20at%20levels%2065%20to%2067%20will%20receive%20two%20weeks%20of%20base%20pay%20per%20six%20months%20of%20service.%20There's%20a%20separate%20package%20for%20executives%20levels%2068%20and%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20also%20offering%20continued%20regular%20stock%20vesting%20for%20six%20or%2012%20months%20for%20levels%2067%20and%20below%2C%20based%20on%20years%20of%20service%2C%20and%20six%20months%20of%20paid%20health%20insurance%20coverage%20plus%20an%20additional%2012%20months%20of%20optional%20COBRA%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20terms%20are%20similar%20to%20those%20the%20company%20offered%20earlier%20this%20year%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-internal-document-shows-buyout-offers-to-us-employees-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVoluntary%20Retirement%20Program%3C%2Fa%3E%20buyouts%2C%20according%20to%20a%20document%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20except%20that%20the%20layoffs%20include%20shorter%20health%20insurance%20coverage%20durations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20layoffs%20come%20as%20Microsoft%20cuts%20costs%20and%20plans%20significant%20spending%2C%20including%20%24190%20billion%20in%20capital%20expenditures%20this%20year%2C%20primarily%20related%20to%20its%20AI%20infrastructure%20buildout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cuts%20mostly%20impact%20the%20sales%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxbox-cuts-employees-with-plans-to-shed-more-workforce-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EXbox%20gaming%20organizations%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Microsoft%20chief%20people%20officer%20Amy%20Coleman%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20employees.%20Microsoft's%20Xbox%20division%20also%20plans%20to%20cut%2020%25%20of%20its%20workforce%20by%20the%20end%20of%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20maximum%20of%2039%20weeks%20of%20severance%20appears%20more%20generous%20than%20offers%20from%20some%20competing%20tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheres-the-standard-severance-package-salesforce-offers-us-employees-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESalesforce%2C%20which%20recently%20conducted%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20a%20standard%20severance%20package%20of%20a%20minimum%20of%20nine%20weeks%20and%20a%20maximum%20of%2030%20weeks%20of%20base%20pay.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-offers-us-workers-up-to-26-weeks-severance-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOracle%20%3Cu%3Eoffered%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20laid-off%20US%20employees%20four%20weeks'%20base%20salary%2C%20plus%20one%20week%20per%20additional%20year%20of%20employment%2C%20up%20to%2026%20weeks%2C%20as%20severance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoff-meta-severance-details-cobra-jobs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20recently%20offered%3C%2Fa%3E%20laid-off%20US%20employees%20a%20severance%20package%20including%2016%20weeks%20%E2%80%94%20or%20four%20months%20%E2%80%94%20in%20base%20pay%2C%20plus%20two%20weeks%20for%20every%20year%20of%20continuous%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aastewart%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eastewart%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20%2B1-425-344-8242.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20ou