%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Olsons%20decided%20to%20save%20as%20they%20established%20their%20careers%20%E2%80%94%20Maddy%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40drivewaymoment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtent%20creator%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20owner%20of%20Over%20Ice%20Soda%2C%20while%20Drew%20works%20in%20commercial%20concrete%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0planning%20to%20buy%20a%20lot%20and%20build%20their%20own%20home%20to%20keep%20mortgage%20payments%20down.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%202025%2C%20the%20Olsons%20finally%20found%20a%20spot%20where%20they%20could%20build%20their%20family%20home.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22984%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20holds%20her%20baby%20up%20in%20front%20of%20a%20grassy%20lot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d478f94175b768171fbe9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221476%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMaddy%20Olson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Olsons%20finally%20made%20the%20jump%20in%20January%202025%2C%20buying%20a%20lot%20for%20%24156%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20lot%20was%20smaller%20than%20they%20had%20hoped%2C%20they%20liked%20the%20location%2C%20as%20it's%20down%20the%20street%20from%20their%20cousin's%20home.%20%26quot%3BIt%20wouldn't%20be%20our%20ideal%2C%20but%20it's%20been%20seven%20years%20of%20thinking%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Olson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOlson%20also%20came%20to%20like%20that%20the%20lot%20size%20ended%20up%20saving%20them%20money%20as%20they%20built%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultigenerational-living-build-wealth-elder-care-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etheir%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20couldn't%20overspend%20if%20we%20wanted%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20easy%20to%20spend%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20and%20make%20it%20beautiful%20without%20having%20to%20spend%20so%20much%20because%20there's%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20space%20to%20build.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBudget%20was%20top%20of%20mind%20for%20the%20Olsons%20as%20they%20built%20their%20home.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22611%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%20kisses%20in%20a%20room%20filled%20with%20construction%20equipment.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d490094175b768171fc03%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221361%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMaddy%20Olson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKeeping%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-built-tiny-home-texas-property-lessons-learned-tips-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuild%20budget%3C%2Fa%3E%20limited%20was%20important%20to%20the%20Olsons%2C%20as%20they%20wanted%20their%20mortgage%20to%20be%20as%20small%20as%20possible.%20They%20set%20their%20budget%20at%20%24209%2C000%20and%20secured%20a%20loan%20for%20the%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20planned%20to%20cut%20costs%20primarily%20by%20doing%20as%20much%20work%20as%20they%20could%20themselves%2C%20saving%20money%20on%20%26quot%3Bsweat%20equity.%26quot%3B%20They%20felt%20confident%20they%20could%20accomplish%20their%20goal%20because%20Drew%20had%20some%20construction%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20his%20first%20time%20doing%20most%20of%20the%20stuff%20in%20our%20house%2C%20but%20he%20has%20a%20general%20knowledge%20of%20how%20to%20use%20most%20tools%2C%26quot%3B%20Olson%20said.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20his%20family%20is%20in%20home%20building.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20hired%20professionals%20to%20handle%20tasks%20like%20installing%20the%20HVAC%20and%20drywall%2C%20but%20the%20Olsons%20said%20they%20did%20basically%20everything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDrew%20works%20for%20his%20parents%2C%20so%20he%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20wiggle%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Olson%20said.%20%26quot%3BOn%20any%20slow%20days%20when%20th