0her%20budget%20as%20she%20designed%20the%20home.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20of%20a%20man%20building%20cabinets%20in%20a%20kitchen%20and%20a%20large%20island%20in%20the%20same%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3047380b873a3c9460cf14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMaddy%20Olson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20they%20were%20working%20with%20a%20limited%20budget%2C%20Olson%20had%20to%20be%20selective%20with%20her%20splurges%20for%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20they%20built%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-renovated-dated-kitchen-photos-budget-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etheir%20kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E%20cabinets%20themselves%20to%20save%20money%2C%20constructing%20them%20at%20home%20after%20the%20manufacturer%20mailed%20them.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20she%20didn't%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20installation%2C%20Olson%20splurged%20on%20a%20Botticelli%20Breccia%20Marble%20countertop%20for%20the%20island%20in%20the%20same%20room.%20The%20island%20cost%20%245%2C700%2C%20a%20price%20Olson%20found%20well%20worth%20it%20for%20the%20pop%20it%20brings%20to%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20my%20prized%20possession%20in%20my%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20splurged%20on%20large%20windows%20to%20bring%20natural%20light%20into%20the%20space%20and%20on%20her%20gold%20doorknobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESome%20of%20Olson's%20favorite%20decor%20pieces%20were%20thrifted.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222817%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20kitchen%20with%20a%20multicolored%20tile%20backsplash%20covering%20the%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d4c9294175b768171fc43%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223756%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3