idn't%20know%20outlet%20locations%20had%20to%20be%20settled%20before%20drywall%20went%20up%2C%20so%20they%20weren't%20as%20intentional%20about%20where%20they%20were%20placed%20as%20they%20would%20have%20been%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20realized%20their%20house%20would%20be%20darker%20than%20they%20wanted%20after%20it%20was%20already%20framed%2C%20so%20Drew%20had%20to%20go%20back%20in%20and%20cut%20more%20windows%20to%20brighten%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20construction%20process%2C%20Olson%20came%20to%20the%20house%20to%20find%20her%20husband%20was%20nearly%20finished%20building%20their%20staircase.%20She%20had%20wanted%20a%20more%20custom%20look%20for%20the%20spindles%2C%20but%20didn't%20realize%20it%20was%20too%20late.%20Luckily%2C%20Drew%20was%20happy%20to%20take%20out%20the%20existing%20structure%20and%20change%20it%20for%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20an%20angel%2C%26quot%3B%20Olson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECommitting%20to%20design%20choices%20was%20also%20tough.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22917%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20cleans%20the%20floor%20tiles%20in%20her%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d535f94175b768171fca5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221633%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMaddy%20Olson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOlson%20also%20said%20she%20struggled%20to%20be%20decisive%2C%20changing%20her%20mind%20after%20trying%20certain%20paints%2C%20light%20fixtures%2C%20or%20even%20tiles.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20video%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40drivewaymoment%2Fvideo%2F7638077906840849694%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20TikTok%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20her%20removing%20tile%20from%20a%20wall%2C%20looking%20at%20it%20after%20it's%20been%20professionally%20painted%2C%20repainting%20it%20after%20she%20didn't%20like%20the%20color%2C%20then%20painting%20it%20%3Cem%3Eagain%3C%2Fem%3E%20after%20that%20color%20didn't%20work%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20found%20herself%20retiling%20rooms%20repeatedly%20and%20buying%20light%20fixtures%20online%2C%20only%20to%20return%20them%20after%20she%20disliked%20how%20they%20looked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20worth%20it%20in%20the%20end%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20cry%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20type%20B%20and%20relaxed%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20my%20house%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20ripped%20out%20tile%20so%20many%20times%20because%20it%20just%20didn't%20look%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Olsons%20finally%20moved%20into%20their%20house%20at%20the%20end%20of%20May%202026.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22862%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20holds%20her%20daughters'%20hands%20as%20they%20walk%20through%20their%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d53975dc133dbf310dcaf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221532%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMaddy%20Olson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%20is%20largely%20finished%2C%20though%20Olson%20said%20they%20are%20still%20fine-tuning%20details%20and%20decorating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20daughter's%20room%20and%20their%20third%20bedroom%20aren't%20decorated%20yet%2C%20and%20it%20will%20take%20some%20time%20to%20get%20them%20in%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20they%20pulled%20off%20the%20renovation%20within%20their%20set%20budget%2C%20keeping%20their%20monthly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-moved-into-garage-apartment-while-starting-business-saved-money-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emortgage%20payments%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20%24900.%20Olson%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bamazing%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Olsons%20hope%20their%20current%20home%20enables%20them%20to%20build%20