0buy%20floor%20models.%20Your%20couch%20could%20be%20on%20the%20sales%20floor%20for%20weeks%2C%20with%20hundreds%20of%20strangers%20sitting%20on%20it%20or%20carts%20bumping%20into%20it%20at%20every%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20may%20be%20some%20hidden%20gems%20at%20a%20reasonable%20price%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20large%20pieces%20that%20will%20get%20lots%20of%20use%2C%20I'm%20not%20willing%20to%20gamble%20on%20quality.%20I'd%20rather%20shop%20at%20dedicated%20furniture%20stores%2C%20like%20a%20CB2%20or%20West%20Elm%2C%20or%20seek%20out%20made-to-order%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20candles%20are%20too%20hit-or-miss%20for%20me.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aisle%20of%20candles%20in%20different%20colors%20and%20sizes%20in%20a%20HomeGoods%20location%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cbe6a50edbc52a864f808%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPaynter%20Rhed%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20candle%20aisle%20at%20HomeGoods%20is%20my%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20whole%20store.%20But%20as%20fun%20as%20the%20section%20is%20to%20peruse%2C%20the%20wide%20variety%20of%20brands%2C%20shapes%2C%20and%20scents%20can%20be%20a%20mixed%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20found%20that%20many%20of%20the%20candles%20I've%20bought%20at%20the%20chain%20either%20don't%20burn%20very%20well%20or%20lose%20their%20scent%20pretty%20quickly%2C%20even%20though%20they%20look%20great%20and%20smelled%20amazing%20in%20the%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20these%20candles%20are%20just%20fine%20in%20a%20pinch%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20might%20get%20lucky%20with%20a%20great%20one%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I'd%20rather%20spend%20more%20to%20buy%20something%20I'm%20confident%20is%20higher%20quality%20from%20an%20actual%20candle%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMany%20of%20the%20large%20mirrors%20don't%20pass%20my%20basic%20quality%20test.%3Cfigu