3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20you%20might%20get%20lucky%20and%20find%20name-brand%20items%20in%20the%20store's%20aisles%2C%20I've%20bought%20many%20random%20pots%20and%20pans%20from%20here%20that%20looked%20nice%20but%20haven't%20held%20up%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20a%20full%2C%20matching%20set%20of%20cookware%20from%20HomeGoods%20is%20also%20tricky%20since%20not%20all%20stores%20carry%20the%20same%20pieces%20or%20multiples%20of%20a%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20supplying%20a%20kitchen%20from%20scratch%20or%20hoping%20to%20build%20a%20collection%2C%20I'd%20rather%20invest%20in%20a%20matching%20set%20from%20a%20trustworthy%20cookware%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESkip%20the%20kitschy%20letters%20and%20signs%20with%20quotes%20and%20phrases%20on%20them.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Large%20letter%20decor%20with%20maps%20within%20them%20and%20desk%20signs%20on%20display%20in%20a%20HomeGoods%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cbfa57a3c8094d5ddbc09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22804%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPaynter%20Rhed%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChoosing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-ways-to-prepare-living-space-for-spring-interior-designer-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperfect%20finishing%20touches%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20space%20can%20be%20one%20of%20the%20trickiest%20tasks.%20However%2C%20I'll%20never%20waste%20money%20on%20hanging%20letters%20or%20signs%20with%20quotes.%20Quotes%20are%20meant%20for%20journals%2C%20not%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20signs%20at%20HomeGoods%20with%20overused%20phrases%20and%20cringeworthy%20quotes.%20Some%20pieces%20with%20basic%20labels%20like%20%26quot%3Bcoffee%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Btea%26quot%3B%20even%20feel%20like%20they're%20paying%20homage%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpopular-