re%20short%20videos%20to%20its%20app%20as%20part%20of%20licensing%20deals%20with%20major%20publishers%2C%20including%20BuzzFeed%20Studios%2C%20Cond%C3%A9%20Nast%2C%20Hearst%20Magazines%2C%20Penske%20Media%2C%20and%20People%20Inc.%2C%20Netflix%20said%20Tuesday.%20Starting%20in%20early%20August%2C%20subscribers%20can%20watch%20videos%20ranging%20from%203%20to%2020%20minutes%20from%20brands%20like%20Bon%20App%C3%A9tit%2C%20Cosmopolitan%2C%20The%20Hollywood%20Reporter%2C%20Variety%2C%20and%20Vogue.%20The%20videos%20center%20on%20topics%20like%20travel%2C%20cooking%2C%20and%20fashion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-stream-bill-simmons-other-popular-video-podcasts-spotify-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvesting%20in%20video%20podcasts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20short-form%20vertical%20video%20to%20better%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-not-netflix-is-big-threat-to-hollywood-analysis-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompete%20with%20YouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20been%20rapidly%20growing%20its%20share%20of%20TV%20viewership%20in%20recent%20years.%20YouTube%20had%20a%2013.4%25%20share%20of%20US%20TV%20viewing%20in%20April%202026%2C%20versus%20Netflix's%207.8%25%2C%20per%20Nielsen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix's%20new%20licensing%20deals%20are%20%26quot%3Bstraight%20out%20of%20the%20YouTube%20handbook%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brandon%20Katz%2C%20the%20insights%20director%20at%20entertainment%20research%20firm%20Greenlight%20Analytics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20another%20attempt%20to%20court%20low-cost%20engagement%20with%20lean-back%20pop%20culture%20programming%2C%26quot%3B%20Katz%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20%26quot%3BNetflix%20is%20trying%20to%20become%20a%20more%20habitual%20source%20of%20entertainment%20without%20having%20to%20pony%20up%20the%20premiums%20for%20hit-or-miss%20original%20programming.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20Hollywood%20streamers%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-disney-short-form-video-youtube-tiktok-hollywood-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleaning%20into%20short-form%20clips%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20in%20hopes%20of%20driving%20higher%20engagement%20and%20training%20users%20to%20open%20their%20apps%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20partnerships%20help%20us%20deepen%20fandom%20and%20create%20more%20ways%20for%20members%20to%20carry%20those%20stories%20with%20them%20throughout%20their%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Derderian%2C%20the%20VP%20of%20Animation%20Series%20and%20Kids%20%26amp%3B%20Family%20TV%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20about%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShort-form%20video%20isn't%20new%20for%20Netflix.%20The%20streaming%20leader%20first%20experimented%20with%20vertical%20clips%20in%202021%20with%20a%20%26quot%3BFast%20Laughs%26quot%3B%20feature%20that%20showed%20snippets%20from%20comedy%20shows.%20Netflix%20shuttered%20the%20feed%20a%20few%20years%20later%2C%20before%20adding%20short-form%20video%20again%20earlier%20this%20year.%20The%20streamer%20has%20also%20had%20videos%20of%20less%20than%20four%20minutes%20as%20part%20of%20its%20%26quot%3BWWE%20Legend%20Profiles%26quot%3B%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20has%20been%20looking%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20addition%20of%20YouTube%20content%20to%20its%20platform%20by%20offering%20publishers%20more%20relaxed%20licensing%20terms%2C%20according%20to%20two%20people%20who've%20had%20direct%20conversations%20with%20the%20streamer%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-video-podcast-push-shows-to-challenge-youtube-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einitial%20push%20to%20add%20podcasts%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202025%2C%20Netflix%20insisted%20that%20podcasters%20pull%20their%20video%20shows%20off%20YouTube.%20That%20would%20be%20a%20tough%20ask%20for%20some%20creators%20and%20publishers%20who've%20built%20big%20businesses%20on%20YouTube.%20(It%20did%20some%20early%20deals%20with%20creators%20like%20Ms.%20Rachel%20that%20didn't%20have%20that%20requirement.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Netflix%20is%20regularly%20talking%20about%20licensing%20shows%20and%20podcasts%20without%20requiring%20them%20to%20leave%20YouTube%2C%20the%20two%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20real%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20involved%20in%20the%20discussions%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20podcasters%20and%20other%20creators%20will%20still%20have%20to%20consider%20whether%20being%20available%20on%20Netflix%20will%20cannibalize%20their%20YouTube%20audience%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20the%20licensing%20fee%20Netflix%20pays%20will%20make%20up%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-short-form-video-licensing-deal-partnership-video-podcasts-youtube-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783450443000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d41e194175b768171fba1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-short-form-video-licensing-deal-partnership-video-podcasts-youtube-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix%20is%20adding%20short%20clips%20from%20publishers%20like%20Cond%C3%A9%20Nast%20in%20a%20deal%20that's%20%26quot%3Bstraight%20out%20of%20the%20YouTube%20handbook%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20one%20analyst%20put%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jfaris%40businessinsider.com%20(James%20Faris%2CLucia%20Moses)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3Bamp%3BK%20HC%20rejects%20Cong%20worker%E2%80%99s%20plea%20to%20shift%20trial%20from%20Srinagar%20to%20Jammu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783450406000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132246547%2Cimgsize-1238902.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fterror-threat-plea-improbable-hc-rejects-cong-workers-plea-to-shift-trial-from-srinagar-to-jammu%2Farticleshow%2F132246534.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20High%20Court%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh%20rejected%20a%20Congress%20worker's%20plea.%20He%20sought%20to%20shift%20his%20cheque%20bounce%20trial%20from%20Srinagar%20to%20Jammu.%20The%20court%20stated%20terrorism%20is%20almost%20eliminated%20in%20the%20Valley%20now.%20It%20noted%20the%20petitioner's%20claims%20of%20threat%20were%20improbable%20and%20lacked%20merit.%20The%20court%20found%20the%20petition%20was%20filed%20to%20avoid%20payment%20and%20prolong%20proceedings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22NASEER%20GANAI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20century-old%20barbecue%20restaurant%20has%20its%20top-secret%20barbecue%20sauce%20recipe%20locked%20in%20a%20bank%20vault%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221904%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McClard's%20Bar-B-Q%20is%20famous%20for%20serving%20Bill%20Clinton%20and%20its%20top-secret%20sauce%20recipe.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d3928965805a2c542daf0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221344%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcClard's%20Bar-B-Q%20is%20famous%20for%20serving%20Bill%20Clinton%20and%20its%20top-secret%20sauce%20recipe.%3Cp%3ELolo%20A.%2FYelp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMcClard's%20has%20kept%20its%20barbecue%20sauce%20recipe%20in%20a%20bank%20vault%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Arkansas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-iconic-famous-barbecue-restaurant-in-every-state%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebarbecue%20restaurant%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20family-owned%20since%201928.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBill%20Clinton%20once%20had%20McClard's%20ribs%20flown%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreek-meatballs-recipe-easy-quick-dinner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efamily%20recipes%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20tucked%20away%20in%20a%20kitchen%20drawer%20or%20written%20down%20in%20a%20dusty%20recipe%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20McClard's%20Bar-B-Q%20in%20Arkansas%2C%20one%20family%20recipe%20is%20considered%20so%20valuable%20that%20it's%20locked%20away%20in%20a%20bank%20vault.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nearly%20century-old%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffranklin-barbecue-austin-texas-review-what-to-order-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebarbecue%20institution%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20serving%20customers%20since%201928%2C%20and%20four%20generations%20of%20the%20McClard%20family%20have%20helped%20preserve%20the%20restaurant's%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20perhaps%20no%20tradition%20is%20more%20closely%20guarded%20than%20the%20recipe%20for%20its%20signature%20barbecue%20sauce%20%E2%80%94%20the%20recipe%20that%20helped%20transform%20a%20roadside%20tourist%20station%20into%20one%20of%20Arkansas'%20most%20beloved%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223928687d-6e84-412e-a70f-89e9bebe5f20%5C%22%3EIts%20top-secret%20barbecue%20sauce%20has%20become%20part%20of%20McClard's%20legendary%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McClard's%20Bar-B-Q%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d36d194175b768171fb44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20McClards%20created%20the%20recipe%20for%20their%20iconic%20barbecue%20sauce%20back%20in%201928.%3Cp%3ENancy%20E.%2FYelp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mcclards.com%2Fmcclards-bbq-history.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestaurant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20founders%20Alex%20and%20Gladys%20McClard%20operated%20the%20Westside%20Tourist%20Court%2C%20which%20included%20a%20gas%20station%20and%20diner%2C%20in%20the%20late%201920s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20traveler%20passing%20through%20couldn't%20pay%20the%20roughly%20%2410%20he%20owed%20after%20staying%20for%20two%20months%2C%20he%20offered%20something%20else%20instead%3A%20a%20recipe%20he%20claimed%20was%20for%20%26quot%3Bthe%20world's%20greatest%20barbecue%20sauce.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant%20said%20the%20McClards%20accepted%20the%20recipe%20in%20lieu%20of%20payment%2C%20thinking%20it%20was%20better%20than%20nothing%2C%20and%20realized%20it%20lived%20up%20to%20the%20traveler's%20promise.%20The%20couple%20began%20tweaking%20it%20to%20suit%20their%20tastes%2C%20and%20before%20long%2C%20their%20barbecue%20business%20became%20the%20standout%20attraction%20of%20their%20tourist%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReviewers%20describe%20the%20sauce%20as%20hot%20and%20spicy%2C%20with%20a%20rich%2C%20vinegary%20base%20layer%20that%20adds%20a%20tangy%20bite%2C%20and%20say%20it's%20more%20similar%20to%20traditional%20Carolina%20barbecue%20sauces%20than%20Texas%20or%20Kansas%20City%20varieties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcClard's%20Bar-B-Q%20opened%20in%201928%20and%20moved%20to%20its%20current%20location%20in%201942.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20keeping%20the%20couple's%20iconic%20barbecue%20sauce%20recipe%20in%20the%20restaurant%20kitchen%2C%20the%20restaurant%20says%20the%20handwritten%20recipe%20is%20still%20stored%20in%20a%20safety%20deposit%20box%20at%20a%20downtown%20Hot%20Springs%20bank%20to%20help%20ensure%20it%20remains%20protected%20for%20future%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcClard's%20still%20prepares%20its%20sides%20from%20longtime%20family%20recipes%2C%20a%20tradition%20that%20has%20attracted%20generations%20of%20loyal%20customers%2C%20including%20presidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2253c7d179-837b-49a3-891e-d77bc19593be%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20McClard's%20most%20famous%20fans%20was%20former%20President%20Bill%20Clinton%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McClard's%20Bar-B-Q%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d365f5dc133dbf310db49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBill%20Clinton%20is%20one%20of%20McClard's%20most%20notable%20fans.%3Cp%3EMarc%20E.%2FYelp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EClinton%2C%20who%20spent%20much%20of%20his%20childhood%20in%20Hot%20Springs%20before%20serving%20as%20Arkansas%20governor%20and%20eventually%20president%2C%20remained%20loyal%20to%20the%20restaurant%20long%20after%20leaving%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20known%20to%20be%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20restaurant's%20spicy%20sauce%2C%20tamale%20spread%2C%20and%20chicken%20wings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetakeout.com%2F1696751%2Fmcclard-bbq-arkansas-bill-clinton%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20Takeout%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20then-president%20would%20have%20McClard's%20ribs%20flown%20to%20DC%20on%20Air%20Force%20One%2C%20and%20they%20were%20even%20served%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcamp-david-presidents-history-photos-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECamp%20David%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20presidential%20retreat%20in%20the%20Catoctin%20Mountains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22622c241e-58bc-467b-8fbd-2b6ac18b1d0a%5C%22%3EMcClard's%20is%20still%20a%20local%20favorite%20nearly%20100%20years%20after%20opening%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McClard's%20Bar-B-Q%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d3149965805a2c542daab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcClard's%20Bar-B-Q.%3Cp%3ELolo%20A.%2FYelp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant's%20website%20said%20the%20new%20generation%20of%20ownership%20at%20McClard's%20continues%20to%20see%20great%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20week%2C%20the%20restaurant%20serves%207%2C000%20pounds%20of%20hickory-smoked%20beef%2C%20pork%2C%20and%20ribs%2C%20250%20gallons%20of%20spicy%20barbecue%20beans%2C%20250%20gallons%20of%20cole%20slaw%2C%203%2C000%20hand-rolled%20hot%20tamales%2C%20and%203%2C000%20pounds%20of%20french%20fries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20began%20as%20payment%20for%20an%20unpaid%20motel%20bill%20has%20become%20one%20of%20Arkansas'%20most%20enduring%20culinary%20traditions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20one%20secret%20the%20McClard%20family%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20letting%20slip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcclards-barbecue-arkansas-sauce-recipe-locked-in-a-bank-vault%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783450316000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d46dd965805a2c542db7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcclards-barbecue-arkansas-sauce-recipe-locked-in-a-bank-vault%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22McClard's%20Bar-B-Q%20in%20Hot%20Springs%2C%20Arkansas%2C%20is%20famously%20the%20go-to%20barbecue%20joint%20of%20former%20President%20Bill%20Clinton.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22emcdowell%40businessinsider.com%20(Erin%20McDowell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Camera%2C%20Israeli%20Officer%20Tosses%20Stun%20Grenade%20Into%20Car%20Carrying%20Palestinians%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20CCTV%20clip%2C%20recorded%20on%20Sunday%20and%20released%20by%20Israeli%20human%20rights%20group%20B'Tselem%2C%20shows%20an%20officer%20confronting%20a%20vehicle%20before%20the%20situation%20quickly%20escalates.%22%2C%22publ