5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20tried%2014%20different%20doughnuts%20from%20Krispy%20Kreme.%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdunkin-doughnut-flavors-ranked-worst-to-best-review%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etried%20every%20doughnut%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20could%20find%20at%20Krispy%20Kreme%20and%20ranked%20them%20from%20worst%20to%20best.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20seasonal%20maple-buttercream%20doughnut%20was%20my%20least%20favorite%20because%20it%20was%20super%20sweet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMany%20of%20Krispy%20Kreme's%20classic%20flavors%20remained%20my%20favorites.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20in%20college%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20my%20roommates%20and%20I%20would%20drive%20about%2045%20minutes%20into%20Virginia%20twice%20a%20month%20to%20stock%20up%20on%20fresh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistory-krispy-kreme-doughnuts-iconic-glazed-ipo-stock-filing-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKrispy%20Kreme%20doughnuts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%2C%20which%20opened%20its%20first%20location%20in%20North%20Carolina%20in%201937%2C%20has%20since%20expanded%20outside%20the%20southeastern%20portion%20of%20the%20US.%20Now%2C%20I'm%20just%20a%20short%20bike%20ride%20away%20from%20multiple%20Krispy%20Kreme%20locations%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20try%20not%20to%20go%20too%20often%20%E2%80%94%20I%20can't%20eat%20doughnuts%20like%20I%20did%20in%20college%20anymore%20%E2%80%94%20I%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20I'm%20picking%20up%20the%20best%20flavors%20the%20chain%20has%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20went%20to%20my%20local%20Krispy%20Kreme%20and%20bought%20one%20of%20every%20type%20of%20doughnut%20they%20had%20in%20stock.%20Here's%20my%20ranking%20of%20all%2014%20doughnuts%2C%20from%20worst%20to%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEditor's%20Note%3A%20This%20post%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20September%202024.%20Although%20many%20seasonal%20flavors%20return%2C%20item%20availability%20is%20subject%20to%20change.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKrispy%20Kreme's%20maple-buttercream%20doughnut%20was%20way%20too%20sweet%20for%20me.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22648%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20glazed%20doughnut%20topped%20with%20thick%20beige%20frosting%20and%20colorful%20sprinkles%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f478010d59cc64f5b0402d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22486%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20limited-time%20seasonal%20variety%2C%20the%20maple-buttercream%20doughnut%20is%20a%20glazed%20yeast%20doughnut%20with%20a%20swirl%20of%20maple%20frosting%20on%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20other%20doughnuts%20I%20tried%20had%20this%20type%20of%20frosting%20%E2%80%94%20most%20of%20the%20others%20had%20icings%20lacquered%20on%2C%20whereas%20this%20was%20piped%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20frosting%20had%20the%20color%20and%20flavor%20of%20maple%20candy%20but%20tasted%20even%20sweeter.%20It%20was%20way%20too%20sugary%20for%20my%20liking%2C%20even%20by%20doughnut%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20oatmeal-Kreme-pie%20flavor%20had%20too%20much%20going%20on.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22736%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20doughnut%20topped%20with%20vanilla%20frosting%2C%20cinnamon%20streusel%2C%20a%20dollop%20of%20cream%2C%20and%20a%20small%20oatmeal%20cookie%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f476d0f9f6733e4bdfa149%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22552%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20oatmeal-Kreme-pie%20flavor%20was%20another%20seasonal%20variety.%20It%20was%20by%20far%20the%20most%20heavily%20dressed%20doughnut%20in%20the%20bunch.%20To%20be%20honest%2C%20it%20looked%20like%20it%20came%20from%20a%20fancy%20bakery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20cream-filled%20option%20was%20topped%20with%20vanilla%20frosting%2C%20streusel%2C%20more%20cream%2C%20and%20a%20little%20oatmeal%20cookie.%20If%20you%20think%20that%20sounds%20like%20too%20much%2C%20you're%20absolutely%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20maple%20buttercream%2C%20this%20doughnut%20was%20cloyingly%20sweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20thought%20the%20strawberry%20doughnut%20with%20sprinkles%20tasted%20artificial.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20doughnut%20topped%20with%20pink%20icing%20and%20colorful%20sprinkles%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f476def9f6733e4bdfa14e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20frosting%20on%20the%20strawberry-iced%20doughnut%20had%20a%20candy-like%20artificial%20flavor%20that%20tasted%20almost%20medicinal.%20It%20even%20turned%20off%20my%204-year-old%2C%20who%20loves%20pink%20things%20and%20sprinkles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20only%20ranked%20it%20this%20highly%20because%20my%207-year-old%20said%20it%20was%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchefs-favorite-doughnuts-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efavorite%20doughnut%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20bunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20didn't%20love%20the%20chocolate-iced%20doughnut.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22664%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20doughnut%20topped%20with%20chocolate%20icing%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f476ea0d59cc64f5b03f3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22498%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20pulled%20the%20chocolate-iced%20doughnut%20out%20of%20the%20box%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20looked%20fairly%20boring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20taking%20a%20bite%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20didn't%20love%20the%20icing.%20The%20flavor%20was%20on%20the%20sweet%20side%2C%20and%20there%20wasn't%20much%20depth%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20kids%20thought%20sprinkles%20made%20the%20standard%20chocolate-iced%20doughnut%20better.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22659%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20doughnut%20topped%20with%20chocolate%20icing%20and%20colorful%20sprinkles%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f476f80d59cc64f5b03f45%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22494%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20doughnut%20was%20exactly%20the%20same%20as%20the%20chocolate-iced%20version%20but%20with%20rainbow%20sprinkles%20on%20top.%20In%20my%20kids'%20eyes%2C%20this%20made%20it%20distinctly%20better%20than%20the%20regular%20chocolate-iced%20doughnut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20eyes%2C%20however%2C%20there%20weren't%20enough%20sprinkles%20to%20make%20much%20difference%20in%20the%20flavor%20or%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20pumpkin-spice%20cake%20doughnut%20was%20a%20nice%20change%20of%20pace.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22634%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dark-colored%20glazed%20doughnut%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f477050d59cc64f5b03f4c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22475%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pumpkin-spice%20cake%20doughnut%20was%20the%20only%20flavor%20I%20tried%20with%20a%20cake%20base%2C%20and%20its%20denser%20texture%20made%20for%20a%20nice%20change%20of%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20liked%20that%20Krispy%20Kreme%20didn't%20go%20overboard%20with%20the%20pumpkin-spice%20flavoring%2C%20which%20can%20be%20off-putting%20when%20it's%20too%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20limited-time%20flavor%20reminded%20me%20of%20an%20apple-cider%20doughnut%20with%20hints%20of%20cinnamon%20and%20nutmeg%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20as%20hearty%20or%20as%20crumbly%20as%20I'd%20like%20a%20cake%20doughnut%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20chocolate-iced%20custard-filled%20doughnut%20is%20Krispy%20Kreme's%20take%20on%20a%20classic%20Boston%20cream.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22729%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20doughnut%20with%20no%20hole%20that's%20topped%20with%20chocolate%20icing%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f477770d59cc64f5b03fb4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22547%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20I'd%20never%20tried%20Krispy%20Kreme's%20take%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdunkin-krispy-kreme-tim-hortons-doughnuts-ranked%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBoston%20cream%20doughnut%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20wasn't%20bad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20custard%20filling%20was%20creamy%2C%20on%20the%20thin%20side%2C%20and%20only%20lightly%20sweet.%20But%20again%2C%20I%20was%20unimpressed%20by%20the%20chocolate%20icing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20enjoyed%20the%20chocolate-iced%20Kreme-filled%20doughnut.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22674%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20doughnut%20with%20no%20hole%20that's%20topped%20with%20chocolate%20icing%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f47799f9f6733e4bdfa1d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22506%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cream%20in%20this%20doughnut%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20filling%20of%20a%20Twinkie%20%E2%80%94%20fluffy%20and%20very%20sweet.%20I%20liked%20that%20it%20kept%20the%20doughnut%20extra%20moist%20and%20sweet%20throughout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20glazed%20lemon-filled%20doughnut%20was%20a%20pleasant%20surprise.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22689%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20glazed%20doughnut%20with%20no%20hole%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f477b2f9f6733e4bdfa207%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22517%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20took%20a%20bite%20of%20this%20doughnut%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20I%20liked%20the%20lemon%20filling.%20It%20was%20closer%20in%20consistency%20to%20custard%20than%20jelly%2C%20and%20it%20had%20a%20nice%20citrusy%20zing%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20order%20this%20again%2C%20even%20though%20I%20don't%20normally%20love%20lemony%20desserts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20kids%20loved%20Krispy%20Kreme's%20cake-batter%20doughnut.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22677%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20doughnut%20with%20no%20hole%20that's%20topped%20with%20yellow%20icing%20and%20colorful%20sprinkles%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f477f0de59ade1a3b4a5a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22508%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%204-year-old%20said%20the%20cake-batter%20doughnut%20was%20her%20favorite%20of%20the%20ones%20she%20tried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20topped%20with%20cheerful%20yellow%20icing%20and%20rainbow%20dot%20sprinkles.%20I%20thought%20the%20cake-batter%20cream%20filling%20tasted%20more%20buttery%20than%20traditional%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20bit%20on%20the%20sweet%20side%20for%20my%20tastes%2C%20but%20I'd%20buy%20it%20again%20and%20give%20it%20to%20the%20kids%20to%20split.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20dulce%20de%20leche%20flavor%20on%20the%20salted-caramel-cheesecake%20doughnut%20was%20delicious.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22669%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20glazed%20doughnut%20topped%20with%20swirls%20of%20brown%20and%20white%20frosting%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f476c3de59ade1a3b4a53c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22501%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seasonal%20salted-caramel-cheesecake%20flavor%20is%20essentially%20a%20glazed%20doughnut%20topped%20with%20swirls%20of%20cream-cheese%20buttercream%20and%20dulce%20de%20leche%20flavoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhotos%20of%20the%20dessert%20make%20it%20look%20like%20it's%20finished%20with%20salted-caramel%20crumbs%2C%20but%20the%20one%20I%20got%20had%20very%20little%20salted%20caramel%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20what%20was%20there%20tasted%20only%20of%20salt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cream-cheese%20buttercream%20mostly%20tasted%20like%20the%20regular%20cream%2C%20but%20the%20dulce%20de%20leche%20flavor%20was%20delicious.%20It%20was%20rich%2C%20buttery%2C%20and%20salty%2C%20which%20went%20well%20with%20the%20sweetness%20of%20the%20glaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%207-year-old%20rejected%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Btoo%20salty%20to%20be%20dessert%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20I'll%20definitely%20look%20out%20for%20this%20variety%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20glazed%20raspberry-filled%20doughnut%20is%20a%20classic%20for%20a%20reason.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20glazed%20doughnut%20with%20no%20hole%20that's%20filled%20with%20raspberry%20jelly%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f4780e0d59cc64f5b04034%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22507%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20glazed%20raspberry-filled%20doughnut%20is%20one%20of%20my%20go-to%20Krispy%20Kreme%20orders%2C%20and%20it%20didn't%20disappoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20what%20to%20expect%3A%20a%20delicious%20mess%20of%20goopy%2C%20tangy%20raspberry%20filling%20and%20the%20chain's%20familiar%20glaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20appeal%20of%20this%20doughnut%20may%20be%20nostalgia%20for%20me%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20reason%20it's%20a%20classic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20loved%20that%20the%20spiced-apple-filled%20doughnut%20was%20topped%20with%20cinnamon%20sugar.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22695%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20doughnut%20with%20no%20hole%20that's%20topped%20with%20granulated%20sugar%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f4781af9f6733e4bdfa279%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22521%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seasonal%20spiced-apple-filled%20doughnut%20was%20the%20only%20one%20I%20tried%20that%20had%20cinnamon%20sugar%20instead%20of%20glaze%20on%20the%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20was%20an%20apple%20filling%20with%20a%20nice%20hint%20of%20warm%20spices.%20It%20tasted%20like%20an%20elevated%20version%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-chains-apple-pie-ranked%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%20apple%20pie%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20original%20glazed%20doughnut%20was%20my%20favorite.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22612%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20glazed%20doughnut%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f47826f9f6733e4bdfa285%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22459%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20taste%20test%2C%20I%20learned%20you%20can't%20go%20wrong%20with%20Krispy%20Kreme's%20classics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20the%20original%20glazed%20doughnuts%20always%20taste%20a%20bit%20fresher%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20K