0with%20him%20and%20him%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20now%20the%20mom%20of%20three%20kids%20ages%208%20and%20under.%20My%20parents%20are%20in%20their%2080s%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20a%20constant%20pull%20to%20be%20there%20for%20all%20of%20them%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2205553009-c57a-4001-ba8d-f73aa92ba383%5C%22%3EI%20moved%20from%20Argentina%20to%20the%20US%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EExactly%2016%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-moving-from-argentina-to-us-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20from%20Argentina%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20I%20am%20from%2C%20to%20the%20US%20to%20attend%20grad%20school.%20My%20intention%20was%20to%20come%20for%20a%20year%20and%20move%20back%20home.%20I%20had%20left%20my%20apartment%2C%20my%20cat%2C%20and%20a%20boyfriend%20who%20said%20he'd%20wait%20for%20me.%20But%20after%20graduating%2C%20I%20got%20a%20job%20that%20sponsored%20my%20visa%2C%20and%20encouraged%20by%20my%20dad%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20living%20in%20the%20US%20a%20try.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20intention%20was%20never%20to%20live%20so%20far%20away%20from%20my%20parents%2C%20but%20one%20thing%20led%20to%20the%20next.%20I%20met%20my%20now%20husband%2C%20we%20had%20kids%2C%20bought%20a%20house%2C%20and%20now%20I%20need%20to%20travel%20almost%2024%20hours%20to%20get%20a%20proper%20hug%20from%20the%20people%20who%20raised%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20see%20my%20parents%20often%2C%20it%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20expensive.%20I%20can%20tell%20how%20quickly%20time%20is%20ticking%20between%20visits.%20My%20mom%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falzheimers-and-dementia-misconceptions-and-surprising-facts-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediagnosed%20with%20Alzheimer's%3C%2Fa%3E%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20while%20her%20condition%20is%20stable%2C%20I%20sometimes%20don't%20recognize%20her.%20My%20dad%20has%20battled%20multiple%20cancers%20throughout%20his%20life%2C%20and%20while%20still%20very%20active%2C%20he%20is%20slowing%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e35053c0-8fbe-474b-bbae-828b417ac394%5C%22%3EI%20carry%20a%20lot%20of%20guilt%20because%20of%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20we're%20in%20breaks%20my%20heart%20because%20I%20want%20to%20be%20with%20them%20for%20the%20mundane%2C%20not%20just%20the%20extravagant%20splurges%20like%20going%20to%20see%20Argentina%20play%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-cup-hospitality-tickets-worth-it-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20World%20Cup%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20just%20in%20case%20it's%20the%20last%20one%20we%20see%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20feel%20guilty%20for%20not%20always%20being%20there%20to%20watch%20my%20kids%20grow%20up.%20It's%20clich%C3%A9%2C%20but%20so%20very%20true%2C%20that%20the%20years%20are%20so%20short%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20look%20back%20at%20photos%20from%20just%20last%20summer%20and%20can%20tell%20how%20quickly%20time%20is%20flying%20by.%20My%208-year-old%20can%20now%20wear%20the%20same%20shoe%20size%20as%20me%2C%20and%20I%20find%20myself%20packing%20boxes%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsustainable-kid-products-diapers-toys-playsets-hand-me-downs-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehand-me-down%20clothes%3C%2Fa%3E%20almost%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b69eff76-01a4-48cb-bc11-4308350ba0d4%5C%22%3EI'm%20being%20pulled%20in%202%20directions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20sure%20being%20an%20only%20child%20exacerbates%20all%20my%20feelings%2C%20but%20I%20also%20know%20I'm%20not%20the%20only%20one%20stuck%20in%20the%20sandwich%20years%20%E2%80%94%20watching%20my%20kids%20growing%20up%20and%20my%20parents%20getting%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20I%20really%20want%20is%20to%20bottle%20up%20all%20the%20fleeting%20moments%20with%20them.%20When%20my%20kids%20ask%20me%20for%20a%20snuggle%20before%20bed%2C%20I%20do%20it%20even%20though%20I%20have%20a%20pile%20of%20laundry%20to%20fold%2C%20because%20one%20day%20they%20won't%20ask%20for%20that%20anymore.%20When%20my%20mom%20calls%20me%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20dinner%2C%20I%20always%20pick%20up%20because%20soon%20she%20might%20not%20know%20how%20to%20use%20a%20phone%20anymore.%20I%20take%20photos%20of%20my%20kids%20doing%20the%20little%20things%2C%20only%20to%20turn%20around%20and%20do%20the%20same%20with%20my%20parents.%20I%20want%20to%20remember%20it%20all%20before%20it's%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pull%20in%20two%20directions%20never%20lets%20up.%20But%20maybe%20that's%20not%20a%20problem%20to%20solve%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20it's%20just%20what%20it%20feels%20like%20to%20be%20this%20loved%2C%20and%20to%20love%20this%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraising-kids-aging-parents-only-child-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783447940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d309e5dc133dbf310db0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraising-kids-aging-parents-only-child-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Living%20thousands%20of%20miles%20from%20my%20parents%20while%20raising%20three%20young%20children%20has%20made%20me%20feel%20pulled%20between%20two%20generations%20I%20love.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpreti%40insider.com%20(Conz%20Preti)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netflix%20Confirms%20Ana%20Mar%C3%ADa%20Londo%C3%B1o%20as%20Head%20of%20Content%2C%20Colombia%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783447866000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236803809%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix%20has%20appointed%20Ana%20Mar%C3%ADa%20Londo%