%2Fa%3E%2C%20operate%20Airbus%20and%20Boeing%20aircraft%20with%20some%20seats%20that%20lack%20physical%20windows%20because%20of%20the%20plane's%20design.%20For%20example%2C%20seats%2010A%20and%2011A%20on%20certain%20Boeing%20737s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20shouldn't%20necessarily%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%20Most%20carriers%20identify%20these%20seats%20during%20the%20booking%20process.%20Still%2C%20air%20carriers'%20ticketing%20of%20these%20seats%20is%20under%20scrutiny%20as%20the%20cases%20proceed%2C%20potentially%20with%20ramifications%20for%20seat%20offerings%20and%20fares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20cases%2C%20both%20filed%20in%20August%202025%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funited-airlines-wants-windowless-window-seats-lawsuit-dismissed-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallege%20that%20United%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Delta%20charged%20passengers%20extra%20for%20these%20seats%20without%20providing%20a%20clear%20warning%20that%20they%20would%20actually%20be%20seated%20beside%20a%20blank%20section%20of%20fuselage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAviva%20Copaken%2C%20a%20plaintiff%20in%20the%20suit%20against%20United%2C%20said%20she%20paid%20up%20to%20%24170%20for%20window%20seats%20that%20did%20not%20have%20a%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20November%20motion%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case%2C%20United%20argued%20that%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpassengers-sue-united-and-delta-over-windowless-window-seats-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewindow%20seat%3C%2Fa%3E%20simply%20refers%20to%20a%20seat%20positioned%20next%20to%20the%20aircraft%20wall%2C%20rather%20than%20one%20that%20guarantees%20a%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224907%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Row%2039%20doesn't%20have%20a%20window%20on%20Iberia's%20A321XLR.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d345c94175b768171fb2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223681%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20is%20an%20example%20of%20a%20windowless%20seat%3A%20row%2039%20on%20Iberia's%20A321XLR.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20US%20district%20judge%20in%20San%20Francisco%20rejected%20that%20motion%20on%20Monday%2C%20allowing%20the%20lawsuit%20to%20move%20forward.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-class-delta-flight-surprising-things-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelta's%20motion%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20dismiss%2C%20which%20was%20filed%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20is%20still%20pending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20future%20ruling%20against%20the%20airlines%20could%20prompt%20them%20and%20other%20carriers%20to%20rethink%20how%20they%20price%20or%20disclose%20these%20seats.%20United%20has%20already%20updated%20its%20booking%20process%20to%20show%20when%20a%20selected%20seat%20lacks%20a%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnited%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20had%20nothing%20to%20share%20regarding%20the%20lawsuit.%20It's%20unclear%20if%20Delta%20updated%20its%20booking%20systems%3B%20the%20airline%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1fef2e1-2daf-4a5e-b0ab-bf7434f227e4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20are%20there%20windowless%20seats%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWindowless%20seats%20are%20largely%20a%20result%20of%20how%20aircraft%20are%20designed%20and%20how%20airlines%20plan%20their%20seat%20layout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAircraft%20such%20as%20the%20Airbus%20A320%2C%20Boeing%20737%2C%20and%20Boeing%20757%20families%20have%20components%2C%20including%20air%20conditioning%20ducts%2C%20emergency%20equipment%2C%20and%20electrical%20wiring%2C%20that%20can%20prevent%20windows%20from%20being%20installed%20in%20certain%20parts%20of%20the%20fuselage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20legroom%20airlines%20want%20to%20give%20their%20passengers%20also%20plays%20a%20role.%20Adding%20or%20removing%20rows%20could%20shift%20the%20alignment%20with%20the%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20location%20of%20windowless%20seats%20varies%20by%20plane%20model%2C%20but%20they%20are%20often%20found%20around%20exit%20rows%20or%20at%20the%20rear%20of%20the%20cabin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbus-a321xlr-iberia-tour-business-class-economy-boston-madrid-2024-11%23there-is-no-window-in-one-row-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpanish%20flag%20carrier%20Iberia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20windowless%20seats%20in%20row%2039%20on%20its%20Airbus%20A321XLRs.%20JetBlue%20has%20at%20least%20one%20no-window%20seat%20on%20much%20of%20its%20Airbus%20narrowbody%20fleet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20larger%20jets%2C%20like%20the%20Boeing%20777%20and%20Boeing%20787%2C%20have%20seats%20with%20misaligned%20windows%20rather%20than%20completely%20missing%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20unpopular%20windowless%20seats%20are%20in%20extra-legroom%20sections%20of%20economy%20and%20can%20cost%20a%20premium%20despite%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20a%20United%20Boeing%20737-900%20flight%20from%20Chicago%20to%20Newark%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20in%20September%20disclosed%20during%20booking%20that%20seat%2011A%20did%20not%20have%20a%20window.%20The%20upgrade%20price%20was%20%2480%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20as%20identical%20seats%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faisle-seats-are-better-than-window-seats-on-flights-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erows%20with%20windows%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20United%20disclosing%20the%20windowless%20seat%20at%20booking.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d30fa965805a2c542daa7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22367%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUnited%20disclosed%20the%20windowless%20seat%20during%20a%20test%20booking.%3Cp%3EUnited%20Airlines%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20pricing%20strategy%20is%20not%20unusual%3A%20looking%20at%20flights%20on%20Alaska%20and%20Ryanair%2C%20windowless%20seats%20were%20priced%20the%20same%20as%20other%20regular%20window%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac93b41e-9e1c-4a6d-b34c-705cc2c26485%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20get%20a%20refund%20for%20booking%20a%20windowless%20seat%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECopaken%2C%20the%20plaintiff%2C%20said%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20that%20United%20refunded%20her%20seat%20fee%20after%20she%20complained%20to%20the%20airline.%20Another%20plaintiff%2C%20Marc%20Brenman%2C%20said%20he%20received%20a%20refund%20of%207%2C500%20MileagePlus%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20refunds%20are%20not%20guaranteed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnited%20said%20its%20contract%20of%20carriage%20does%20not%20define%20a%20window%20seat%20as%20providing%20an%20external%20view%2C%20and%20refunds%20are%20generally%20required%20only%20when%20a%20customer%20is%20downgraded%20from%20their%20original%20paid%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20policies%20exist%20at%20other%20airlines%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-class-flight-alaska-airlines-not-worth-it-basically-economy-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincluding%20Alaska%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20JetBlue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20may%20be%20worth%20asking%20an%20airline%20for%20a%20refund%20or%20travel%20credit%20if%20you%20discover%20your%20window%20seat%20is%20actually%20a%20blank%20wall%2C%20passengers%20may%20have%20limited%20recourse%20if%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20window%20was%20disclosed%20at%20the%20time%20of%20booking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-some-airline-window-seats-dont-have-windows-united-delta-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783446884000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d2ecb94175b768171fade%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww