s%20without%20our%20youngest%20and%20make%20memories%20that%20will%20stick%20with%20him%20is%20limited.%20Although%20I%20hope%20to%20be%20healthy%20and%20spry%20for%20many%20more%20years%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20I%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20here%20and%20now%20because%20the%20future%20is%20uncertain.%20Even%20with%20the%20best%20possible%20outcome%2C%20there%20will%20be%20fewer%20tomorrows%20than%20I%20would%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b68d9c33-8921-4e86-bb3c-d42b753d3b3b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeeing%20a%20World%20Cup%20match%20was%20a%20chance%20to%20give%20my%20son%20an%20experience%20he%20will%20never%20forget%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fson-mom-soccer-fan-world-cup-tickets-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enever%20been%20into%20sports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emy%20son%20loves%20soccer.%20He%20taught%20me%20to%20derive%20a%20lot%20of%20joy%20from%20watching%20him%20play%2C%20cheering%20for%20his%20favorite%20club%2C%20Real%20Madrid%2C%20and%20seeing%20our%20local%20team%2C%20DC%20United%2C%20in%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hard%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20make%20his%20dreams%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-cup-hospitality-tickets-worth-it-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eseeing%20a%20World%20Cup%20match%3C%2Fa%3E%20come%20true%20until%20Visit%20Sugar%20Land%2C%20the%20tourism%20bureau%20of%20Sugar%20Land%2C%20Texas%2C%20just%20outside%20of%20Houston%2C%20invited%20us%20to%20see%20a%20match.%20The%20entire%20day%20exceeded%20all%20of%20our%20expectations%2C%20and%20I%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20stadium%20knowing%20that%20my%20son%20had%20an%20experience%20he%20will%20never%20forget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20son%20at%20a%20World%20Cup%20game.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d2e9d965805a2c542da80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20that%20nothing%20compares%20to%20the%20excitement%20of%20being%20at%20a%20stadium%20for%20a%20World%20Cup%20match.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jamie%20Davis%20Smith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20match%2C%20I%20called%20my%20husband%20to%20tell%20him%20that%20there%20was%20nothing%20like%20being%20at%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20person%2C%20watching%20our%20soccer-fanatic%20son%20drink%20in%20every%20moment%2C%20sharing%20the%20drama%20of%20every%20moment.%20%26quot%3BI%20wish%20you%20could%20have%20been%20there%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20told%20him.%20%26quot%3BI%20wish%20all%20of%20us%20could%20see%20a%20match%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b0554e5-469a-4ff9-8270-ca7c5fecfe7a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERacing%20against%20time%20sometimes%20means%20splurging%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20checked%20the%20calendar%20to%20see%20if%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20could%20take%20our%20son%20to%20another%20game%20during%20our%20packed%20summer.%20There%20was%20one%20match%20in%20my%20hometown%20of%20Philadelphia%20that%20was%20feasible.%20It%20wasn't%20cheap%20or%20something%20we%20had%20budgeted%20for%2C%20but%20it%20was%20only%20a%20three-hour%20drive%20away%2C%20and%20we%20could%20stay%20with%20family%20to%20keep%20costs%20down.%20I%20started%20asking%20friends%20for%20advice.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20will%20the%20World%20Cup%20be%20in%20the%20United%20States%20again%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20another.%20%26quot%3BMy%20husband's%20best%20childhood%20memories%20are%20going%20to%20the%20World%20Cup%20with%20his%20Dad%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20friend%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20he%20still%20loves%20soccer%20and%20watches%20with%20our%20girls%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20still%20on%20the%20fence%20because%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-cup-so-expensive-5-charts-ticket-prices-hotels-flights-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20decided%20to%20go%20into%20planning%20mode%20in%20earnest.%20When%20I%20saw%20tickets%20pop%20up%20during%20FIFA's%20last-minute%20ticket%20sale%2C%20I%20panic-bought%20three%20seats%2C%20paying%20more%20than%20double%20what%20I%20expected.%20I%20also%20got%20access%20to%20a%20hospitality%20suite%2C%20which%20I%20knew%20would%20make%20the%20game%20extra%20special.%20After%20I%20hit%20buy%2C%20I%20had%20a%20twinge%20of%20regret.%20However%2C%20I%20reminded%20myself%20that%20as%20an%20older%20parent%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20ensure%20my%20family%20has%20incredible%20experiences%20now%2C%20while%20we%20can.%20Sometimes%20that%20means%20dipping%20into%20savings%20or%20going%20out%20without%20other%20material%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20(right)%20with%20her%20HUsband%20and%20their%20son%20at%20a%20World%20Cup%20game.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d2e6e965805a2c542da7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(right)%20said%20she%20is%20happy%20that%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20got%20to%20experience%20the%202026%20World%20Cup%20with%20their%20youngest%20child.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jamie%20Davis%20Smith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cae005b1-8207-4cff-868e-4e7785d78f45%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaving%20incredible%20experiences%20with%20my%20kids%20while%20I%20can%20is%20always%20worth%20the%20trade-off%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-eras-tour-brought-mother-teen-daughter-closer-together-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincredible%20experiences%20with%20my%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20always%20worth%20the%20time%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20investment.%20Seeing%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20Philadelphia%20was%20no%20exception.%20My%20heart%20was%20full%20as%20I%20watched%20my%20husband%20and%20son%20enjoy%20the%20day.%20Getting%20to%20be%20by%20my%20son's%20side%20as%20he%20smiled%20and%20screamed%2C%20fully%20in%20his%20element%2C%20was%20worth%20the%20splurge.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThanks%20to%20our%20access%20to%20a%20hospitality%20suite%2C%20we%20got%20to%20hold%20a%20match%20ball%20and%20pose%20with%20the%20World%20Cup%20trophy%2C%20making%20the%20day%20even%20more%20special.%20%26quot%3BMessi%20touched%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20son%20said%20as%20he%20posed%20for%20a%20photo.%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20Christiano%20Rolandlo%20gets%20it%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20emphasizing%20his%20loyalty%20to%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-citizenship-in-european-countries-through-ancestry-as-american%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPortuguese%20mom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Plus%2C%20having%20access%20to%20an%20air-conditioned%20lounge%20with%20easy%20access%20to%20ice-cold%20drinks%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20nicer%20than%20I%20anticipated%2C%20since%20the%20game%20we%20saw%20was%20one%20of%20the%20hottest%20in%20World%20Cup%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20that%20my%20son%20will%20carry%20the%20memories%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20game%20he%20witnessed%20with%20his%20Dad%20and%20me%20long%20after%20we%20are%20gone.%20I%20hope%20his%20memories%20of%20the%20day%20will%20forever%20make%20him%20smile%20as%20much%20as%20he%20did%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20match%2C%20and%20that%20is%20priceless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-parent-splurging-to-make-memories-with-child-world-cup-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783443257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d2dcf94175b768171fad6%3Fformat%