ad%20of%20just%20parts%20of%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20the%20concept%20raised%20eyebrows.%20Could%20yarn%20really%20replace%20the%20fragrance%20and%20grandeur%20of%20roses%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20response%20was%20mixed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ananya%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20people%20loved%20the%20concept%20of%20forever%20sustainable%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20whereas%20others%20still%20preferred%20fresh%20flowers%20because%20of%20their%20elegance.%20It%20took%20time%20for%20people%20to%20warm%20up%2C%20but%20now%20we%E2%80%99re%20seeing%20far%20more%20queries%20compared%20to%20last%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20this%20surge%2C%20she%20explains%2C%20comes%20from%20the%20diaspora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMostly%2C%20the%20NRIs%20are%20really%20loving%20the%20concept.%20It%20has%20this%20delicate%2C%20niche%20quality%20and%20connects%20them%20back%20to%20their%20heritage.%20They%20also%20appreciate%20the%20custom%20options%2C%20different%20flowers%2C%20pearls%2C%20and%20colour%20schemes%2C%20which%20allow%20them%20to%20personalise%20in%20a%20way%20fresh%20flowers%20often%20can%E2%80%99t.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335040%2Fgujarat-padma-pareekh-runs-pb-handmades-crochet-handicraft-small-business-senior-citizen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Etakes%20between%2014%20to%2020%20hours%20to%20complete%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20design.%20The%20process%20begins%20with%20careful%20planning%3A%20the%20right%20flower%20size%2C%20the%20right%20colours%2C%20the%20right%20balance%20of%20pearls%20and%20embellishments.%20Once%20the%20prototype%20is%20approved%2C%20her%20team%20of%2025%20underprivileged%20women%20artisans%20from%20Uttarakhand%20gets%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanya%20Setia%E2%80%99s%20Gul%20is%20another%20powerhouse%