0children%20started%20participating%20eagerly.%20They%20even%20role-played%20as%20teachers%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20police%20officers.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20classroom%20filled%20with%20laughter%20and%20energy.%20When%20the%20children%20laugh%20and%20play%2C%20they%20learn%20without%20even%20realising%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sangeeta%2C%20these%20moments%20are%20priceless.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20child%20tells%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20want%20to%20be%20a%20teacher%20like%20you%2C%E2%80%99%20my%20heart%20swells%20with%20pride.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBalancing%20two%20worlds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20school%2C%20Sangeeta%20is%20a%20mother%20and%20wife.%20Married%20in%20Azamgarh%2C%20with%20her%20parental%20home%20in%20Raebareli%2C%20she%20balances%20household%20responsibilities%20with%20teaching.%20Her%20son%2C%20now%20seven%2C%20once%20had%20clashing%20school%20timings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sangeeta%20fulfills%20multiple%20roles%20from%20mentor%20to%20friend%2C%20crucially%20adapting%20her%20skills%20to%20meet%20the%20varied%20needs%20of%20her%20students.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-17